{"tid":2283448,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"揭荒唐釘牌罪名！教師引教局教材爛gag「造紙棄寫龜板防絕種」 反遭教局斥「無稽」","createTime":"2020-11-12T14:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T14:36:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b99fb2ea6a7f9ccd9c9f187c2ff8cde5376e37b4","tid":2283448,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"教育局稱該名教師在教學時稱古人研發紙張的目的，說成是代替龜板、動物骨頭等做記錄以「防止動物絕種」是「無稽之談」。教協總幹事沈偉男在Facebook貼出上述影片截圖，稱「荒謬的是，這個無稽之談，是出自教育局的教育電視」，又指即使教師有錯，也不可能去到要終身取消教師資格的地步。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》已向教育局查詢，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/TIITYXWHV5FRXOCKRHMSGGGTOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2FTIITYXWHV5FRXOCKRHMSGGGTOY%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BylA4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=1f42fc37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2FTIITYXWHV5FRXOCKRHMSGGGTOY%2F&h=f93aa79d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/TIITYXWHV5FRXOCKRHMSGGGTOY/</a>"}]}